Param files:

    param        - melt of 100 chains of 8 atoms.
    param_a_d    - same as param, but uses program mdSim_a_d with angles and dihedrals enabled.
    param_np     -  ideal gas, otherwise similar to param

Command files:

    commands     - used by param and param_a_d,  reads ../in/config
    commands_np  - used by param_np (ideal gas), reads ../in/config_np

Input files (directory in/)

    config    - equilibrated interacting system, used with param and param_a_d
    config_np - equilibrated ideal gas, used with param_np

